                <div class="col-md-5 mt-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center">Stress Management</h2>
                    <hr class="my-2">
                    <p class="text-primary font-weight-bold">
                            Stress is an inevitable part of everyone’s lives. What causes us stress may vary from person to person, but the fact remains that we all face some kind of stress or another. While stress cannot be completely eliminated, what we do to manage and control feeling stressed is called stress management.
                    </p>
                    <blockquote class="blockquote text-center">
                            <p class="text-primary font-weight-bold font-italic">
                                    Stress management could include yoga, meditation, breathing exercises, going for a walk, listening to music, taking part in sports, playing with a pet, changing our thinking and learning to say no, talking to friends and many more.
                            </p>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
        </div>
    
      

